Requirements
------------

* linux or bsd system
* PHP 5.2
* pdo_sqlite

Running All The Benchmarks
--------------------------

    > php TestRunner.php

Running One Of The Benchmarks
-----------------------------

    > cd propel_15
    > php TestRunner.php

Test Scenarii
-------------

1. Mass insertion: Tests model objects and save() operations.

2. Retrieve By Pk: Tests basic hydration

3. Basic Query with 5 results: Tests Query parsing and collections

3. Query with join: Tests join hydration